    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine currently struggles to stay idle and there are noticeable leaks throughout the undercarriage. Cosmmetically, the body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn in several places. It is best suited for someone looking for a major restoration project or a donor vehicle for parts.",
